{"id": 514, "genre": 1001, "title": "别人对你的家乡都存在怎样的误解？", "description": "微博上说关于青岛人每次吃饭都是一整桌海鲜，作为青岛人的我表示钱包扛不住。", "record_count": 7062, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021838217uwKJkL4dNp9DngC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-03T10:51:22Z", "options": [{"id": 10496, "content": "我说我是张家口人他们问我哪里是不是风景特别好啊他们都以为是张家界", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149261}, {"id": 10498, "content": "海南人全都会游泳。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172121}, {"id": 11011, "content": "广东人很抠门", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173570}, {"id": 11012, "content": "江苏高考，考！345就本一！400就能上北大！拜托！我们总分才480！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178901}, {"id": 10501, "content": "安徽人都是乞丐   这句话说出来的时候 有没有想过我会把你摁着打", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139373}, {"id": 10502, "content": "东北人成天干仗", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176225}, {"id": 13320, "content": "我真的觉得大家对河南的地域歧视让我觉得心寒，坏人哪都有，好人也遍地是，因为一些人一些事就否定一个城市，最可笑的行为。哦对了，我不是河南人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205098}, {"id": 13321, "content": "山西人都是挖煤的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205098}, {"id": 10506, "content": "台州人很低调。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174329}, {"id": 10508, "content": "山西人都是土豪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176099}, {"id": 10764, "content": "内蒙人都住蒙古包，能喝酒，骑马上学", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234957mT5qbo04M7V2xSw3.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177509}, {"id": 11276, "content": "浙江有钱人多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181318}, {"id": 10509, "content": "四川人素质都低，有事没事就撕逼打锤过孽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176352}, {"id": 11021, "content": "红烧狮子头并非沧州特产。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149319}, {"id": 11279, "content": "都骑骆驼上学 一月只洗一次澡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181331}, {"id": 24847, "content": "中国人都会打乒乓 会武功", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304203}, {"id": 10769, "content": "贵州人都特别穷 住的地方都没电 天天都唱山歌玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177511}, {"id": 10773, "content": "北京就是高大上北京人日常衣着分分钟上红毯……别逗了好吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177577}, {"id": 11030, "content": "湖南人天天参加快乐大本营", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122938}, {"id": 21526, "content": "你们山西人小时候是不是都是骑着驴翻好几座山去上学啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267513}, {"id": 10263, "content": "啊，你是陕西人呀，蔬菜只吃过土豆是吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 10519, "content": "说自己家乡的事，让大家解释其他地方的人误解自己家乡的一些事情，说着说着怎么变成责怪其他地方了？你们说其他地方的事情，反而印证了你们对其他地方的误解，其他地方的人也说你们所在地方的你认为是错误的事情，结果呢，满屏的负能量，没有一个真实的东西，这个话题偏了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146403}, {"id": 10264, "content": "东北？大酸菜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 10520, "content": "说什么，满屏的全是对其他地方的误解，全是负能量。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146403}, {"id": 10265, "content": "广东，吃老鼠吧，还有小孩儿什么的（煲仔饭）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 428, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 10266, "content": "四川人没事吃花椒玩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 171, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 10522, "content": "解释在哪里，不要让别人一直误解，也不要一直误解别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146403}, {"id": 10779, "content": "浙江人都很有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177595}, {"id": 10780, "content": "胡建能的普通发", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211209HyQatW492IxNLjDw.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177570}, {"id": 10782, "content": "住的离海边很近我就一定得会游泳吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177597}, {"id": 11550, "content": "浙江人很有钱???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183961}, {"id": 11296, "content": "潮汕人 大男子主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162060}, {"id": 10785, "content": "四川人喝的水都是辣的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177181}, {"id": 11300, "content": "潮汕人特能生小孩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181373}, {"id": 10791, "content": "宝宝们。东北虽然夏热冬冷。但是我们冬天暖气开起来能热到你尖叫。大街上没有打架的。冬天水果店也要啥有啥。买东西方便到你不敢相信。另外，呵呵，反正我没见过赵本山?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177643}, {"id": 10792, "content": "广西人都贫困", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177635}, {"id": 10537, "content": "我们枣庄没有枣！！！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170660}, {"id": 10793, "content": "北方人不吃米饭，天天只吃馒头", "image": "img/option/option/201606052120489QwVYqgC1GhvLuBo.jpg", "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169039}, {"id": 11305, "content": "天津人每天一张嘴就说相声。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181439}, {"id": 11563, "content": "内蒙那里四季常青蓝天白云小羊清河马驹吃草", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128917}, {"id": 11052, "content": "贵州是昆明的省会城市，给跪了，不光地理老师要吐血，原因你们懂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178747}, {"id": 10544, "content": "内蒙古人都骑马上学住蒙古包会射箭还会说蒙古语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131830}, {"id": 13618, "content": "江苏妹纸都是很温柔。不可能。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209567}, {"id": 20277, "content": "海鲜便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269601}, {"id": 10295, "content": "长沙人啊，天天都吃臭豆腐吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172291}, {"id": 10296, "content": "一天不上辣椒憋得慌", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173539}, {"id": 10297, "content": "上海人特别没种还老搞歧视。", "image": null, "praise_count": 519, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 76083}, {"id": 12089, "content": "广东人什么都吃。除了贝爷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188511}, {"id": 10298, "content": "早年有人觉得我们骑着骆驼上班上学", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 15674, "content": "胡建人的普通话是笑话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217385}]}